    <title>Lamb tagine pasties</title>
    <updated>2026-03-30T16:38:25.454503+00:00</updated>
    <content type="html">&lt;h1 style="text-align:center;font-family:sans-serif;"&gt;Lamb tagine pasties&lt;/h1&gt;
        &lt;br&gt;
        &lt;img src="https://www.strangerfoods.org/images/lamb-tagine-pasties.webp" style="text-align:center;"/&gt;
        &lt;br&gt;
        &lt;p style="font-family:sans-serif;&gt;I’m a big fan of North African food so to me it makes complete sense to fill a pasty full of spicy, aromatic lamb tagine. At home, these only last a matter of minutes, so expect these pasties to be a big hit!&lt;/p&gt;</content>
